}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== <small>Linksys is marketing this as AX4500 but it is not yet clear where this number comes from.</small>
"P/N:141911720075J HQ1" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
FCC documents claim that the [[Linksys MR9600 v1]] is internally identical.
* Web GUI: https://linksyssmartwifi.com
